3) Office Products: The charger can also be used in office settings, making it relevant to the office products category.
4) Tools & Home Improvement: Similar to the second point, the charger can be considered a tool for improving home functionality.
5) Industrial & Scientific: The charger can be used in industrial settings for charging batteries, making it relevant to the industrial and scientific category.
